Nigerian musician, Davido, also known as David Adeleke has recalled days when he and his brothers lived without money. The singer said his visit to his old apartment in the United States brought back old memories of hardship. According to him, at that point in time, what was left of him was the dream he had to make it big. Davido said 12 years later, he is now a millionaire and fast approaching becoming a billionaire. He tweeted, “Damn I went to my old apartments where I used to live 12 years ago with Sina and B red! “As hard as it is to believe .. we had no money, no support just us and a dream !! 12 years later ! We millions in ! Road to a billion !!! We thank God !! Never stop believing!”